doctype html
html
  head
    title Tatort Subtitle Converter &amp; Translator
  body
    div.app

      h1 Tatort Subtitle Converter &amp; Translator
      p.subheadline A little tool, to find the subtitle file in the given URL, to download it, so it can translate in into the given language and provide a download-Link.

      form(action="/generate", method="post")
        div
          label(for="web-url") Web-Address
          input(type="text", name="url", id="web-url")
          small Note: This must be the URL of the Video-Page, not the overview.
        div
          label(for="target-language") Language
          select(name="targetlang")
            option(value="en", selected) English
            option(value="fr") French
            option(value="de") German
        div.submit
          button(type="submit", name="save") Generate

      h2 Available Translations
      ul
        each translation in translations
          li
            a(href="/subtitles/" + translation)= translation

    style(type="text/css").
      body {
        background-color: #F5F5F5;
        color: #333;
        font-family: Arial;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .app {
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 1rem;
        width: 29rem;
      }

      h1 {
        border-bottom: 1px solid #E1E1E1;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin: 0 0 .8rem 0;
        padding: 0 0 .3rem 0;
      }

      h2 {
        border-bottom: 1px solid #E1E1E1;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin: 2rem 0 .8rem 0;
        padding: 0 0 .3rem 0;
      }

      h1,
      h2 {
        font-weight: normal;
      }

      a {
        color: #3E77DB;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover,
      a:focus {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      label {
        display: block;
        font-size: .8rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: .5rem;
      }

      small {
        color: #B9B9B9;
        font-size: .7rem;
      }

      ul {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      ul > li {
        padding: .2rem 0;
      }

      form {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      form > div {
        display: inline-block;
        max-width: 20rem;
        padding: 0 2rem 0 0;
        vertical-align: top;
      }

      form > div.submit {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      input {
        border: 1px solid #D4D4D4;
        padding: .2rem;
        width: 100%;
      }

      input:focus {
        border: 1px solid #3E77DB;
      }

      button {
        background-color: #3E77DB;
        border: none;
        color: #FFF;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding: .4rem 1rem;
      }

      button:hover,
      button:focus {
        background-color: #3060B4;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      button:active {
        background-color: #193463;
      }
